The '''University of Pangalactic Cultural Studies''' was a branch of the [[Lorrd University]] on [[Lorrd/Legends|Lorrd]]. It specialized in how local myths and legends merged with those of other [[Planet/Legends|worlds]] due to interplanetary influences. [[Movac Arisster]] and [[Heilan Rotham]] tenured there.

